<div class="mainnlbt">
    <h1>有什么经典的语句</h1>
    <div class="mainnlbtms">
        <span>类别：<a href="/jingdianyulu/">经典语录</a></span>
        <span>日期：2016-12-23</span>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="cont_wz1">
